description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you a PET-CT Radiographer/Technologist looking for a new challenge?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are currently recruiting for a PET-CT Radiographer/ Technologist to join our Mobile PET CT team.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;InHealth are providers of diagnostic and healthcare services to the NHS and Private providers. Through our range of Radiology Services, Pathway Services and Screening Services, we see more than 2 million patients a year across the UK.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our primary goal is to make healthcare better by providing rapid and accurate assessment of every patient’s condition, enabling the right treatment to be delivered swiftly and effectively by specialist providers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As one of the UK’s leading experts in the provision of PET-CT solutions, we are experienced in providing patients with accessible, modern and efficient scans when and where they are needed, linking results and reports to the relevant cancer network.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What does being a &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PET-CT Radiographer/ Technologist involve?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is &lt;strong&gt;37.5 hours &lt;/strong&gt;per week &lt;strong&gt;Monday – Sundayas per local rota.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a PET-CT Technologist at InHealth, you will be undertaking PET CT imaging procedures efficiently and effectively for both the public and private sectors; adhering to best practice of radiographic technique. Maintaining a high level of professionalism and technical standard of work, complying with relevant Codes of Practice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Skills and Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BSc Radiography or BSc Nuclear Medicine&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience within PET-CT or Nuclear Medicine is essential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic appreciation of patient care and knowledge of the requirements of a radiographer / technologist’s role in the care of patients, their visitors and carers, and to colleagues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work in a multidisciplinary team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous basic use of imaging equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Safety awareness skills utilising imaging equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional and cooperative attitude towards patients, customers and colleagues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven competency in verbal and written communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with Imaging Equipment in a clinical environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexibility to work the shifts required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be prepared to undertake National travel to attend training courses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What can InHealth offer you?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer a highly competitive salary and a generous flexible benefits package, including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;27 days holiday plus bank holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private medical healthcare with Bupa&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company pension scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gym membership discount&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plus many more!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer you the opportunity to do something you love, with the right support to access the roles you want, through clear career paths and best-in-class training and development. This is an environment where you have accountability for your career and can make a real contribution to the organization and to our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;InHealth is an equal opportunities employer and welcomes applications from all areas of the community.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Some of our roles will be subject to DBS criminal record checking in line with legal requirements but don’t worry; we will guide you through this if you are offered a role with us.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are a great place to work!! Thank you for your interest in working with InHealth.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
